{"tid":1576143,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"麗晶花園街坊遭裝修師傅圍打反被控","createTime":"2019-09-17T06:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T06:48:05.000Z","uid":6261,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5372cb22fe9560938ff6d674271c444b73bef450","tid":1576143,"uid":6261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:11:19.000Z","msg":"早上10點左右，麗晶花園1座18樓窗外裝修時疑因跌下石碎，街坊要求停工及叫保安處理，幾分鐘後，一位自稱老闆的裝修師傅到場與街坊口角，約互罵五分鐘後，兩位裝修師傅下樓圍打街坊，需要街坊及保安阻止，警方到場落口供及查看CCTV後，黑衫街坊及橙衫裝修師傅分別乘救護車往聯合醫院。<br />\n<br />\n黑衫街坊在醫院等待驗傷時，被控公眾地方打架，麗晶區議員畢東尼前往理解情況。<br />\n<br />\n而家報警既下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de832633ac0cce5b3928eb9a6d5636ed65830c12","tid":1576143,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"3956cb1e0cd41eeab9636d605017079a6bd1524f","tid":1576143,"uid":19728,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:13:40.000Z","msg":"其實不嬲都係咁<br />\n喺香港畀人打<br />\n一還手就兩邊一齊告公眾地方打鬥"},{"pid":"1e5406b932950d3087d811028776841e0b3dea88","tid":1576143,"uid":52928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"正常call勞記"},{"pid":"b7161f02587380fecd1572bf4d6145c58144a459","tid":1576143,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"香港原來唔俾打交咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5473a32d09fd